177 A.3d 111 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. ANTHONY AURIEMMA, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-409 September Term 2017

079630 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001399-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
